<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Command Center | AstroDataHub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --accent: #2563eb;
            --bg-admin: #f8fafc;
            --text-main: #0f172a;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --success: #10b981;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-admin);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .admin-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* Header Style */
        .admin-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .admin-header h1 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Stats Bar */
        .admin-stats-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .stat-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-box span { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; }
        .stat-box h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 5px 0 0; color: var(--accent); }

        /* Grid Layout */
        .admin-dashboard-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .admin-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .admin-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .admin-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }

        .admin-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .btn-action {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-action:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-logout {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #ef4444;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .btn-logout:hover { background: #fecaca; }

        /* Special highlight card */
        .highlight-card {
            border: 2px solid #dbeafe;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #eff6ff);
        }

        /* Broadcast Card Style */
        .broadcast-card {
            border: 1px solid #10b981;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #f0fdf4);
        }
        
        .broadcast-icon {
            position: absolute;
            right: -10px;
            top: -10px;
            font-size: 4rem;
            opacity: 0.05;
            transform: rotate(15deg);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="admin-container">
        
        <div class="admin-header">
            <div>
                <p style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0;">Administrative Portal</p>
                <h1>Welcome, <%= adminUser.username %></h1>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
                <a href="/" class="btn-action" style="padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.85rem;">View Site</a>
                <form action="/auth/logout" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-logout">Logout</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="admin-stats-row">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span>Total Users</span>
                <h2><%= stats && stats.totalUsers ? stats.totalUsers : '1,248' %></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span>Active Enrollments</span>
                <h2><%= stats && stats.totalEnrollments ? stats.totalEnrollments : '432' %></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span>Courses Published</span>
                <h2><%= stats && stats.totalCourses ? stats.totalCourses : '18' %></h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="admin-dashboard-grid">
            <div class="admin-card">
                <h3>User Management</h3>
                <p>Manage student accounts across all tiers (Nursery to Research). View progress or handle permissions.</p>
                <a href="/admin/manage-users" class="btn-action">Manage Students</a>
            </div>

            <div class="admin-card">
                <h3>Curriculum Manager</h3>
                <p>Create and edit lessons for school subjects, advanced sciences, and specialized math courses.</p>
                <a href="/admin/manage-courses" class="btn-action">Edit Courses</a>
            </div>

            <div class="admin-card broadcast-card">
                <div class="broadcast-icon">üì°</div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <h3 style="margin:0;">Global Broadcast</h3>
                    <span style="background: var(--success); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;">Live</span>
                </div>
                <p>Transmit instant notifications to every registered user. Use for announcements or site updates.</p>
                <a href="/admin/broadcast" class="btn-action" style="background: var(--success); color: white;">Send Transmission</a>
            </div>

            <div class="admin-card highlight-card">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <h3 style="margin:0;">Daily Discovery</h3>
                    <span style="font-size: 1.2rem;">üí°</span>
                </div>
                <p>Update the "Fun Fact" that appears on every student's dashboard to keep them engaged daily.</p>
                <a href="/admin/manage-fact" class="btn-action" style="background: var(--accent); color: white;">Update Fun Fact</a>
            </div>
            <div class="admin-card" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);">
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <h3 style="margin:0;">Quiz Assessment</h3>
        <span style="font-size: 1.2rem;">üìù</span>
    </div>
    <p>Deploy interactive quizzes to specific modules to test student knowledge and award bonus XP.</p>
    <a href="/admin/manage-courses" class="btn-action">Configure Quizzes</a>
</div>

            <div class="admin-card">
                <h3>Analytics Hub</h3>
                <p>Monitor platform growth, popular subjects, and student completion rates.</p>
                <a href="/admin/analytics" class="btn-action">View Reports</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>